<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11644</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17519</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那个男人走进了唐僧的房间。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17520</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22725</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你……你……你是谁？”唐僧紧张地问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22726</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26987</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是乌鸡国的国王。”男人说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26988</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32396</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“五年前，我的国家遭遇了一场可怕的旱灾。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32397</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37532</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>庄稼不再生长，我的百姓都要饿死了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37533</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40998</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有一天，一个道士来到我的国家。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40999</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45988</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他说他有很强的法力，可以求雨。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45989</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50260</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那道士求来雨了吗？”唐僧问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50261</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54632</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>国王点点头。“雨下了好几天，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54633</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58180</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们的庄稼又开始生长了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58181</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61988</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“很好啊！”唐僧笑着说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61989</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65997</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，他的笑容又马上消失了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65998</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70161</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不太明白。你为什么让我帮你呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70162</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73665</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>国王叹了口气说：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73666</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78131</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“后来，我和那道士成了很好的朋友。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78132</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81182</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有一天，我们正在散步。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81183</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84502</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我看到井里发出了奇怪的光。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84503</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87713</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我走到井边，朝里面看去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87714</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91849</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，我就被人推了下去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91850</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94884</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>是那个道士干的！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94885</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98583</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他用法力弄出光来骗我。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98584</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104072</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我掉进了井里，他封住井口。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104073</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109078</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>国王流着眼泪，继续说道：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109079</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111929</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的身体还在井底。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111930</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116904</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我……我现在只是个鬼魂。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116905</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120248</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“太可怕了！”唐僧说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120249</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123979</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您的护卫一定惩罚了那个道士吧？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123980</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129503</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>国王摇摇头说：“那道士变成了我的样子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129504</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135056</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在，每个人都认为他是真正的国王。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135057</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141447</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>国王停了一下说：“从此，我就一直在冥界。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141448</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145790</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>今晚，是一位神仙带我来见你的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145791</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148398</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他说你可以帮我。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148399</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151844</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我怎么才能帮你呢？”唐僧问，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151845</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154905</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我只是个和尚。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154906</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161231</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的，但孙悟空也和你一起来了。”国王说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161232</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165989</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“孙悟空很厉害。他可以打败那个道士！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165990</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168472</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧犹豫了一下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168473</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172115</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“悟空不能冲进宫里去打那个道士。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172116</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175239</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>人们会认为悟空是妖怪，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175240</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178224</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>而且没有理由地打国王。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178225</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181405</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的儿子，也就是王子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181406</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185297</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他可以把你们带进宫去。”国王说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185298</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189790</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那时，孙悟空就可以暗中打那个道士了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189791</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194103</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们要去哪里找王子呢？”唐僧问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194104</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198643</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他明天会出宫打猎。”国王说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198644</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202098</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你把我说的一切告诉他就行了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202099</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205744</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他不会相信我们的。”唐僧说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205745</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208986</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他以为那道士是他父亲。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208987</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213506</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“给他看这个。”国王拿出了一块玉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213507</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216501</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是我唯一的皇家珍宝。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216502</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218450</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我的儿子一看到它，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218451</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221593</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就会知道你们说的是真的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221594</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，国王看了一下门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225036</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>231091</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那神仙在叫我。我得走了。”国王消失了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>231092</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234292</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧叫来了他的徒弟们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234293</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236985</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们迅速跑进了房间。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236986</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241326</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧把国王说的一切告诉了他们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241327</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244655</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他给我看了一块玉。”唐僧说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244656</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246861</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他四处看了看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246862</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250325</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不知道现在那块玉在哪里。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250326</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254553</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那只是一个梦而已。”悟空说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254554</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>256581</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不，那不是梦。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>256582</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260473</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧边说边在房间里到处找。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260474</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>262200</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他走出了房间。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>262201</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>265536</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>其他人也跟着他走了出去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>265537</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>270120</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“在那里！”门边的地上有一块玉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>270121</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>276756</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天一早，王子出宫打猎。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>276757</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>282234</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看到了一只小白兔，便射了一箭。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>282235</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>287181</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他射偏了，那兔子跑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>287182</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>293051</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>王子追着小白兔跑进了寺院。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>293052</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>298282</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在寺院里，王子看到了一个和尚、一头猪，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>298283</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>302382</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>还有一个穿着紫色衣服的神仙。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>302383</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>306437</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那兔子变成了一只猴子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>306438</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>310639</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这到底是怎么回事？”王子大声说道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>75</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>310640</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>316043</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧上前一步，说：“不要害怕，王子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>76</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>316044</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>322325</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们有事情要告诉你。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>